WEBVTT

00:01.718 --> 00:03.747
There is an alternate universe,

00:03.847 --> 00:05.898
and in it
another version of us.

00:05.961 --> 00:07.628
Previously on <i>Fringe...</i>

00:07.713 --> 00:09.297
We know who our
enemy is now.

00:09.381 --> 00:11.015
His name is
David Robert Jones.

00:11.082 --> 00:12.266
He's a scientist.

00:12.351 --> 00:13.634
Jones is responsible

00:13.719 --> 00:15.169
for dosing Agent Dunham
with Cortexiphan.

00:15.237 --> 00:16.754
For what purpose?

00:16.805 --> 00:18.589
He was trying to activate
some kind of latent ability.

00:18.640 --> 00:19.857
What are you doing,
Olivia?

00:19.925 --> 00:21.959
I'm turning on
the lights.

00:22.027 --> 00:26.097
I have discovered David Robert
Jones' true intentions.

00:26.165 --> 00:29.817
Jones is trying to collapse
both universes.

00:29.902 --> 00:31.452
Mutual destruction.

00:31.537 --> 00:35.656
And create a world designed
and controlled by him.

00:35.741 --> 00:37.041
Any way to stop Jones?

00:37.108 --> 00:39.410
I'm afraid we have
to close the bridge.

00:47.519 --> 00:49.620
I think
I shall miss them.

