Hi, Neal.

01:19.067 --> 01:21.986
Cafe mocha, 1%,
no whip?

01:22.053 --> 01:22.987
- That's it.
- Jill, can you

01:23.054 --> 01:24.188
get that started?

01:24.239 --> 01:26.157
That'll be $4.80.

01:38.337 --> 01:41.289
<i>Enjoy.</i>

02:09.533 --> 02:13.120
Are you okay?

02:42.467 --> 02:44.318
<i>What's happening to them?</i>

02:44.403 --> 02:46.487
<i>Don't move.</i>

02:46.571 --> 02:50.140
I think when they move,
they die.

02:53.328 --> 02:56.330
Nobody move!

